Coinbase's average
daily visitors

01:08:07.880 --> 01:08:10.400
is you can see that
a highest read chart

01:08:10.400 --> 01:08:11.990
compared to their volume.

01:08:11.990 --> 01:08:14.920
They probably have
legitimate use.

01:08:14.920 --> 01:08:19.890
The two, ZB and EXX,
